rows.label: qev055104_MSG0001
rows.name:
Perhaps this explains the strange restlessness of my
Ovah as of late.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055104_MSG0003
rows.name: My Ovah is restless, and not for the first time...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055104_MSG0004
rows.name:
The last was just before one of us was executed by the
Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055104_MSG0005
rows.name:
I do not know what will happen, but I am certain that
my Ovah is telling me the future is headed toward an
unfavorable outcome.[ST:wait ]
